{%- comment -%}
  Shelzy's Designs - Font Preloading Snippet

  FONT STRATEGY:
  - Montserrat: Headings, titles, display text (modern sans-serif)
  - Inter: Body text, buttons, navigation, UI elements (clean sans-serif)

  HOW TO USE:
  Add this line to your theme.liquid <head> section:
  {% render 'shelzys-fonts' %}
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%} Preconnect to Google Fonts for faster loading {%- endcomment -%}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

{%- comment -%} Load brand fonts: Montserrat (headings) + Inter (body) {%- endcomment -%}
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Montserrat:wght@500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

{%- comment -%} Load brand CSS {%- endcomment -%}
{{ 'shelzys-brand.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
